des: Groovy Reflections Radio plays mainly sixties and seventies songs in different genres, rock and roll, classic rock, pop, psychedelic, garage, folk, girl group, reggae, crooner classics, and country. We pride ourselves on providing songs that you may have forgotten, songs that should have been hit tunes, tunes big in Europe but not in the states, and choice album cuts. 100% GRoovy!
